<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l20">Mawrers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jn beſant / vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l21"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> gar <expan>ernſtlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit Jm geredt / . vnd als er klagt / daʒ es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l22">vaſte ſein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>derb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wer / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jn geheiſʒen / daʒ er darvmb <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
